OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FThe security guard who allegedly made
OL,8,Fan 11-year-old girl cry for staring at
OL,9,Fpop star Chappell Roan has accepted
OL,10,F"full responsibility".
OL,12,FThe Pink Pony Club singer is facing
OL,13,Fcriticism after being accused of
OL,14,Fordering her security guard to berate
OL,15,Fthe girl and her mother at a hotel in
OL,16,FSao Paulo, Brazil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
