OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FThe story came to light after former
OL,8,FChelsea and Arsenal midfielder
OL,9,FJorginho took to social media last
OL,10,Fweekend to accuse the security guard
OL,11,Fof speaking "in an extremely
OL,12,Faggressive manner" to his wife,
OL,13,FCatherine Harding, and stepdaughter.
OL,15,FHarding, who it is believed shares her
OL,16,Fdaughter with ex-partner and actor
OL,17,FJude Law, has since supported her
OL,18,Fhusband's depiction of events, while
OL,19,Fthe singer and the security guard are
OL,20,Fsharing their own side of the story as
OL,21,Fwell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
