OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FSo what really happened at the Sao
OL,8,FPaulo hotel? ITV News explains.
OL,10,FHow did the feud begin?
OL,12,FJorginho, who currently plays for
OL,13,FFlamengo in Rio de Janeiro, said he
OL,14,Fhad been staying at the same hotel as
OL,15,FRoan with his wife and stepdaughter,
OL,16,Fwhen the incident took place on Sunday.
OL,18,FThe footballer said his stepdaughter
OL,19,Fwas a big fan of the singer, and was
OL,20,Flooking forward to seeing her perform
OL,21,Fat the Lollapalooza festival in Brazil.
OL,26,@oD@atp
