OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FJorginho claimed she recognised the
OL,8,Fsinger at a nearby table at breakfast,
OL,9,Fand smiled at her while walking past
OL,10,Fher table.
OL,12,F"The artist walked past their table.
OL,13,FMy daughter, like any child, got
OL,14,Fexcited and just wanted to make sure
OL,15,Fit was really her," he wrote. "She
OL,16,Fsimply walked past the singer's table,
OL,17,Flooked to confirm it was her, and went
OL,18,Fback to sit with her mum."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
