OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,F"What happened next was completely
OL,8,Fdisproportionate," he wrote, going on
OL,9,Fto claim Roan's personal security had
OL,10,Fberated his wife and child, demanding
OL,11,Fthey not "disrespect" or "harass" the
OL,12,Fpop star.
OL,14,FHe added: "He even said he would file
OL,15,Fa complaint against them with the
OL,16,Fhotel, while my 11-year-old daughter
OL,17,Fwas sitting there in tears. My
OL,18,Fdaughter was extremely shaken and
OL,19,Fcried a lot."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
