OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FWhile Jorginho did say he understood
OL,8,Fthe importance of boundaries, he
OL,9,Ffinished his post with a direct
OL,10,Fmessage to Chappell Roan: "WITHOUT
OL,11,FYOUR FANS, YOU WOULD BE NOTHING. AND
OL,12,FTO THE FANS, SHE DOES NOT DESERVE YOUR
OL,13,FAFFECTION."
OL,15,FA lifetime ban
OL,17,FFollowing the incident, Jorginho said
OL,18,Fhis family decided not to attend the
OL,19,Fconcert Roan was playing at.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
