OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FJorginho's wife, Harding, said on
OL,8,Fsocial media: "This was Ada's reaction
OL,9,Fyesterday to arriving to watch Sabrina
OL,10,FCarpenter.
OL,12,F"Our daughter decided she didn't want
OL,13,Fto go to the show tonight after how we
OL,14,Fwere treated... so instead we had a
OL,15,Fgirls day shopping and then out to
OL,16,Fdinner.
OL,18,F"Thank you everyone for the kind
OL,19,Fmessages, all is well!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
