OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FThe incident - which went viral on
OL,8,Fsocial media - has even led to
OL,9,Fpoliticians in Brazil getting involved.
OL,11,FFollowing Jorginho's post, the Mayor
OL,12,Fof Rio de Janeiro wrote that he was
OL,13,Fbanning the singer from Rio's Todo
OL,14,FMundo no Rio music festival, inviting
OL,15,Fthe 11-year-old girl as a guest of
OL,16,Fhonour instead.
OL,18,F"I mean that as long as I'm in charge
OL,19,Fof our city - this young lady Chappell
OL,20,FRoan will never perform at Todo Mundo
OL,21,Fno Rio!
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
