OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FFollowing the allegations, Chappell
OL,8,FRoan posted her own version of events
OL,9,Fin a video on her Instagram story.
OL,11,FIn it, she denied anyone had
OL,12,Fapproached her, and claimed to have
OL,13,Fnot seen any mother or child.
OL,15,F"No one came up to me. No one bothered
OL,16,Fme. Like, I was just sitting at
OL,17,Fbreakfast in my hotel," she said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@WO]
