OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,F"They did not come up to me. They
OL,8,Fweren't doing anything. It's unfair
OL,9,Ffor security to just assume someone
OL,10,Fdoesn't have good intentions when they
OL,11,Fhave no reason to believe."
OL,13,FShe continued: "I do not hate people
OL,14,Fwho are fans of my music. I do not
OL,15,Fhate children. Like, that is crazy.
OL,17,F"I'm sorry to the mother and child
OL,18,Fthat someone was assuming something
OL,19,Fthat you would do something, and that
OL,20,Fif she felt uncomfortable, it makes me
OL,21,Freally sad. You did not deserve that."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@[O]uD@POU}D@fO]
