OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FMum speaks out
OL,9,FCatherine Harding, posted her own
OL,10,Fstatement on social media disputing
OL,11,Fthe singer's own recollection.
OL,13,F"She literally didn't do anything; she
OL,14,Fjust looked at her and smiled,"
OL,15,FHarding said of her daughter.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
