OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,F"She came back, and she actually said
OL,8,Fto me, 'mum, I don't know if it's
OL,9,Fher.' Because obviously, she looked
OL,10,Flike, you know, with her costumes and
OL,11,Feverything, she looks a little bit
OL,12,Fdifferent.
OL,14,FSpeaking about the security guard who
OL,15,Fapproached them, Harding said: "Even
OL,16,Fif she did send him or she didn't send
OL,17,Fhim, I don't know, for me it felt like
OL,18,Fit really overstepped a boundary."
OL,20,FAn end to the speculation
