OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FOn Thursday, in a statement posted on
OL,8,FInstagram, the security guard involved
OL,9,Fin the incident finally spoke out.
OL,11,FCelebrity bodyguard Pascal Duvier said
OL,12,Fhe was working for another, unnamed
OL,13,Findividual at the time of the
OL,14,Finteraction.
OL,16,F"I do not normally address online
OL,17,Frumours, but the accusations currently
OL,18,Fcirculating are false and constitute
OL,19,Fdefamation. I take full responsibility
OL,20,Ffor the interactions on March 21," he
OL,21,Fwrote.
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
