OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,F"I was at the hotel on behalf of
OL,8,Fanother individual, and I was not part
OL,9,Fof the personal security team of
OL,10,FChappell Roan. The actions I took were
OL,11,Fnot on behalf of Chappell Roan, her
OL,12,Fpersonal security team, her
OL,13,Fmanagement, or any other individuals."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@fO]
