OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FDuvier added: "I made a judgment call
OL,8,Fbased on information we obtained from
OL,9,Fthe hotel, events I had witnessed in
OL,10,Fthe days prior and the heightened
OL,11,Foverall security risk of our location.
OL,12,FMy sole interaction with the mother
OL,13,Fwas calm and with good intentions, and
OL,14,Fthe outcome of the encounter is
OL,15,Fregretful."
OL,17,FThe internet reacts
OL,19,FFollowing the posts, social media was
OL,20,Fawash with people parodying the
OL,21,Fincident.
