OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FUsers were quick to post jokes, with
OL,8,Fit quickly evolving into a meme poking
OL,9,Ffun at how seriously people were
OL,10,Freacting to a seemingly innocuous
OL,11,Fevent.
OL,13,FVideos also began to surface online,
OL,14,Fclaiming to show the singer directing
OL,15,Fher security to intervene when she saw
OL,16,Fpeople filming her while not
OL,17,Fperforming.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
