OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,FSeveral other fans jumped to her
OL,8,Fdefence with stories of the singer
OL,9,Facting kindly towards them when
OL,10,Fapproached.
OL,12,FChappell Roan has previously spoken
OL,13,Fabout boundaries with fans, leading to
OL,14,Faccusations of being ungrateful for
OL,15,Fher fame.
OL,17,FIn 2024 she said in one video: "I
OL,18,Fdon't care that abuse and harassment,
OL,19,Fstalking, whatever, is a normal thing
OL,20,Fto do to people who are famous or a
OL,21,Flittle famous.
OL,26,@yD@`OU
