OL,3,CJorginho, Jude Law and Chappell Roan:
OL,4,CWhat's behind the internet's latest
OL,5,Cdrama?
OL,7,F"It's weird how people think that you
OL,8,Fknow a person because you see them
OL,9,Fonline and you listen to the art they
OL,10,Fmake... I'm allowed to say no to
OL,11,Fcreepy behaviour, okay?"
OL,13,FShe also previously called out what
OL,14,Fshe called the "predatory behaviour"
OL,15,Fof so-called "superfans", and hit back
OL,16,Fat photographers who yelled at her on
OL,17,Fthe VMAs red carpet.
OL,19,FThe Grammy-winning singer is known for
OL,20,Fher tracks including Good Luck, Babe!,
OL,21,FHot To Go!, and Red Wine Supernova.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]
